Hello,

Up for sale is a really nice Orval Overall American Beauty 350 No Frame, graded a 70/5.5 by SGC.

This is the highest graded SGC card and PSA only shows one higher at a 6 (no other 5.5s). A PSA 5 sold for $900 from Heritage in April.

Asking $SOLD net to me (PP/ff preferred), shipping included. Let me know if any questions.

Thanks!
Thanks! This card’s artwork is definitely one of my favorites in the set!
